{"tid":1912444,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"無線：A股已進入牛市","createTime":"2020-03-06T05:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T06:48:50.000Z","uid":239510,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26d6faffb6a22cd3f996073fc8b1738eb6f8d3d0","tid":1912444,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日係公司既電視播無線 見到<br />\n無線請個支那分析師上來<br />\n然後話 支央會大幅放水<br />\nA股必定會進入牛市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又贏<br />\n<br />\nPS 忍笑忍得好辛苦啊 屌你老母"},{"pid":"4becde0687debdd0699bfc6e217e00a8d088c11f","tid":1912444,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8cbafe2d39f05029f21150b306081a521b69328","tid":1912444,"uid":163881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"PMI 仲低過08海潚同人講入牛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5033abd4d1dba839f74697bf0280bdfe5c53484d","tid":1912444,"uid":163881,"l